01:25:32,548 --> 01:25:34,956
在洛杉矶,
他们那么急着
In Los Angeles, they were so anxious

978
01:25:35,051 --> 01:25:38,336
证明他们比其他人
更懂得你的小秘密
to show they understood
your secret thoughts.

979
01:25:38,429 --> 01:25:42,130
佩特西!
我很高兴我有好多小秘密
- Patsy!
- And I was just glad I had some.

980
01:25:42,266 --> 01:25:45,137
亲爱的,你的电话
Honey, there's
a telephone call for you.

981
01:25:46,896 --> 01:25:48,011
你好
Hello.

982
01:25:49,106 --> 01:25:50,933
噢,嗨, 佛莱普
你好吗?
Oh, hi, Flap. How are you?

983
01:25:52,109 --> 01:25:53,936
我很好
I'm fine.

984
01:25:57,365 --> 01:26:00,781
像其他人那样,我看起来变老了
她没有
- I look older, like everyone else.
- She does not.

985
01:26:02,328 --> 01:26:06,491
佛莱普, 你还是那意思
我不认为那是好事
Flap, you sound the same and I'm not
sure that's such a good thing.

986
01:26:07,542 --> 01:26:09,581
是的,她在这里
Yeah, she's right here.

987
01:26:10,503 --> 01:26:14,002
不,除了你,
我们有其他东西可谈
No, we have other things
to talk about besides you.

988
01:26:19,220 --> 01:26:20,797
喂?
Hello?

989
01:26:22,014 --> 01:26:23,425
我没事
I'm fine.

990
01:26:25,476 --> 01:26:28,643
怎么了?
要痛改前非?
What's up? Feeling contrite?

991
01:26:30,856 --> 01:26:34,060
看起来你还没明白
我看到你们在一起
You don't seem to understand.
I saw you together.

992
01:26:35,444 --> 01:26:37,567
什么?
What?

993
01:26:38,739 --> 01:26:42,654
你知道的,
我难以相信你对我们做了这些
You know, Flap, I can't believe
you're doing this to us.

994
01:26:44,537 --> 01:26:46,944
我觉得你太坏了
Well, I think you're spiteful,

995
01:26:47,039 --> 01:26:50,408
我不知道那是在什么时候发生的
and I don't know
when the hell that happened.

996
01:26:51,752 --> 01:26:55,003
不! 再见,我要--
再见
No! Goodbye. I'll... Goodbye.

997
01:27:04,891 --> 01:27:09,967
佛莱普接受了
那份大学系主任的工作
下星期我们搬家
Flap accepted the job at Kearney,
Nebraska. We're moving in a week.

998
01:27:10,062 --> 01:27:12,102
我不明白你为什么不离开他
I don't know why you don't leave him.

999
01:27:12,189 --> 01:27:15,808
老实说,我也不知道
他很可爱
Honestly, I don't know, either.
He's cute.

1000
01:27:37,048 --> 01:27:39,717
整个礼拜我都在整理东西
I've been packing for us all week.

1001
01:27:48,476 --> 01:27:51,145
还记得她爸爸
Sure remembers her daddy.

1002
01:27:53,147 --> 01:27:55,603
你还生气吗?
So, are you gonna stay mad?

1003
01:27:55,691 --> 01:28:00,437
没得到我允许前搬家
我该发点小脾气吧,难道不对吗?
I think being uprooted without my
consent is worth a pout, don't you?

1004
01:28:05,493 --> 01:28:07,984
算了吧
Come on.

1005
01:28:08,079 --> 01:28:10,451
系主任
我知道
- Head of the department.
- I know.

1006
01:28:10,539 --> 01:28:12,164
这里
Here.

1007
01:28:18,464 --> 01:28:22,592
奥罗拉?
盖瑞特,我回来了
- Aurora?
- Garrett! I'm back here.

1008
01:28:24,053 --> 01:28:26,544
嘿,你好啊,陌生人
Well, hello, stranger.

1009
01:28:26,639 --> 01:28:28,881
两天过得怎么样?
What's it been, about two days?

1010
01:28:30,935 --> 01:28:33,343
你家人还在?
Your family still around?

1011
01:28:34,021 --> 01:28:36,061
不,已经走了
No, they left.

1012
01:28:39,902 --> 01:28:41,729
什么?
What?

1013
01:28:54,917 --> 01:28:59,460
你可能知道我要说什么
You probably know
what I'm going to say.

1014
01:29:00,756 --> 01:29:04,339
不,也许不知道
我不希望知道
Oh, maybe not. I hope not.

1015
01:29:08,306 --> 01:29:10,512
嗯,
Well...

1016
01:29:11,225 --> 01:29:17,098
你是那一类女人,
而我可能不是那一类男人,
You're some kind of woman,
but I'm the wrong kind of man,

1017
01:29:17,189 --> 01:29:21,982
看起来我所追求的那一类
and it doesn't look like my shot
at being the right kind is...

1018
01:29:22,069 --> 01:29:25,106
不是正如我所想的
as good as I was hoping for.

1019
01:29:28,951 --> 01:29:31,869
你不明白我有多想你
You don't even know how much
you'll miss me.

1020
01:29:33,039 --> 01:29:35,577
我不想把你踢飞
I don't want to blow smoke
up your ass.

1021
01:29:35,666 --> 01:29:39,711
噢!这是怎么种解脱
Oh! What a relief.

1022
01:29:41,589 --> 01:29:45,587
这只是开始让我
觉得要担起责任来
It's just that I'm starting
to feel an obligation here.

1023
01:29:45,676 --> 01:29:50,006
感觉很难,
尤其是当邻居
It makes it rough,
especially living next door.

1024
01:29:50,097 --> 01:29:53,763
我开始思考
我得注意我的一举--
I'm starting to think
I gotta watch what I'm doing...

1025
01:30:09,283 --> 01:30:12,735
我会想念你
I... I am gonna miss you...

1026
01:30:14,038 --> 01:30:16,078
我感觉很糟糕
and I do feel bad.

1027
01:30:21,170 --> 01:30:23,626
你很幸运
You're lucky.

1028
01:30:24,757 --> 01:30:26,880
我感觉被羞辱了
I feel humiliated.

1029
01:30:52,660 --> 01:30:54,736
能要一张照片吗?
Can I have a picture of you?

1030
01:30:54,829 --> 01:30:57,746
是的,但我只有一张照片了
那里面也有佛莱普
Yeah, but the only one I have
has Flap in it.

1031
01:30:57,832 --> 01:30:59,706
没关系
I don't mind.

1032
01:31:20,563 --> 01:31:22,602
来,亲我一口
Come here, give me a kiss.

1033
01:31:55,389 --> 01:31:58,426
当你完成后,
我需要这类的磁带
When you finish,
I need this kind of type.

1034
01:31:58,517 --> 01:32:01,554
你好, 艾玛
嗨,宝贝
Hello, Emma. Hi, baby.

1035
01:32:02,521 --> 01:32:05,095
她想她爸爸看她穿好衣服的样子
She wanted her daddy
to see her dressed up.

1036
01:32:05,191 --> 01:32:07,267
他随时都会到
He'll be here any minute.

1037
01:32:07,360 --> 01:32:09,518
一会我再和你谈
好的
- I'll talk to you later.
- OK.

1038
01:32:13,115 --> 01:32:14,526
对不起
Excuse me.

1039
01:32:23,834 --> 01:32:26,408
小姐?
Miss?

1040
01:32:26,504 --> 01:32:28,247
小姐?
Miss?

1041
01:32:37,473 --> 01:32:40,924
别让我一直追着你
我有个小孩
Don't make me run after you,
I have a toddler here!

1042
01:33:05,293 --> 01:33:08,543
你是我们来
内布拉斯加的原因吗?
Are you the reason
that we came to Nebraska?

1043
01:33:09,630 --> 01:33:12,002
我想那应该
由佛莱普来回答你
I think that Flap should talk to you.

1044
01:33:13,259 --> 01:33:15,382
我们谈谈吧
We discussed that.

1045
01:33:15,469 --> 01:33:19,218
在他和你谈之前,
我不想和你说话,除非我认为
I don't want to say anything
until he does, except that

1046
01:33:19,307 --> 01:33:24,549
你们之间不再有感情
但我现在无法确认
I don't think there's an emotion
you're having I couldn't... validate.

1047
01:33:31,736 --> 01:33:33,645
告诉你
Tell you what.

1048
01:33:33,738 --> 01:33:37,237
如果你见到佛莱普,
告诉他,他妻子和孩子
If you see Flap,
tell him his wife and his baby

1049
01:33:37,325 --> 01:33:39,650
去打针了,好吗?
went to get their flu shots,
all right?

1050
01:33:39,744 --> 01:33:41,783
你为什么不那样做?
Why don't you do that?

1051
01:33:46,959 --> 01:33:48,833
就这样保持
Just hold still.

1052
01:33:50,213 --> 01:33:51,623
乖孩子
That's a good girl.

1053
01:33:51,714 --> 01:33:55,249
好了?都完了吗
结束了
OK? You're all finished.
It's all over.

1054
01:33:56,260 --> 01:34:00,388
如果你觉得好些了,
轮到妈咪了
If it makes you feel any better,
Mommy's getting a shot, too.

1055
01:34:01,390 --> 01:34:03,964
她能吃泡泡糖吗?
可以
- Can I give her a pop?
- Sure.

1056
01:34:04,060 --> 01:34:06,432
这边
去一边玩吧
- Here.
- There you go.

1057
01:34:08,940 --> 01:34:11,976
如果我丈夫打电话来,
他们会告诉我吗？
Are they gonna tell me
if my husband calls?

1058
01:34:13,569 --> 01:34:15,728
你手臂上有硬块
You have a lump in your armpit.

1059
01:34:15,821 --> 01:34:18,739
多久了?
我不知道
- How long has it been there?
- I don't know.

1060
01:34:18,824 --> 01:34:21,113
梅尔尼,别去踢柜子!
Melanie, stop kicking the cabinet!

1061
01:34:21,202 --> 01:34:24,653
有两个,
但都不算大
There's two of them.
It's not very big, though.

1062
01:34:24,747 --> 01:34:28,496
我要离开城里,
但你不能再等下去
I have to be out of town next week
but you shouldn't wait.

1063
01:34:28,584 --> 01:34:30,162
它们应该被取出来
They should come out.

1064
01:34:30,253 --> 01:34:33,337
取出来?
我该为此担心吗?
Come out? Should I be scared?

1065
01:34:33,422 --> 01:34:39,212
如果你担心,
那么你会高兴
发现其实什么事也没有
If you're scared, you'll be happier
when it turns out to be nothing.

1066
01:34:39,303 --> 01:34:43,799
布吉医生,
妈妈也该奖励块泡泡糖
Dr Butch, Mom should get a pop, too,
for her shot.

1067
01:34:44,892 --> 01:34:48,178
对给,妈咪
谢谢, 梅尔
- Right. Here, Mom.
- Thanks, Mel.

1068
01:34:48,813 --> 01:34:50,687
我知道这是什么
Well, I know what it is.

1069
01:34:50,773 --> 01:34:54,391
你的毛囊堵塞
You don't keep yourself up
so your sweat glands are clogged.

1070
01:34:54,485 --> 01:34:56,644
这是胞囊
那么我就不需要担心了?
- It's a cyst.
- So I shouldn't worry?

1071
01:34:56,737 --> 01:34:59,655
是胞囊,
就在脂肪腺边上
It's a cyst,
right where your oil glands are.

1072
01:34:59,740 --> 01:35:04,449
你吃的东西不对,
也没学会该怎么洗
You never knew how to eat right
and you've never learned how to wash.

1073
01:35:04,537 --> 01:35:07,158
你是对的,谢谢
和梅尔尼讲几句
You're right. Thanks.
Talk to Melanie.

1074
01:35:07,248 --> 01:35:08,825
说"嗨",
嗨!
- Say hi.
- Hi.

1075
01:35:08,916 --> 01:35:11,751
你好
我给你邮了衬衣
Hello, how are you?
I sent you a blouse.

1076
01:35:11,836 --> 01:35:13,627
说"再见"
再见!
- Say goodbye.
- Bye.

1077
01:35:13,713 --> 01:35:18,624
好说--
代我向妈咪告别
OK. Say good...
Say goodbye to your mother.

1078
01:35:26,225 --> 01:35:28,052
她叫什么名字?
What's her name?

1079
01:35:28,144 --> 01:35:31,643
珍妮丝。
医生怎么说?
Janice. What did the doctor say?

1080
01:35:31,731 --> 01:35:36,856
告诉你, 佛莱普
他想尽快把它取出来
I told you, Flap. It's scary
that he wants to do it so fast.

1081
01:35:36,944 --> 01:35:39,518
珍妮丝, 拿着小文件夹
Janice... with her little folder.

1082
01:35:39,614 --> 01:35:44,026
"除非他说了,否则我什么也不说
我们已经讨论过了,佛莱普和我"
"I can't say anything until he does.
We've discussed it, Flap and I."

1083
01:35:44,118 --> 01:35:48,116
真的吗, 佛莱普!
"验证我的感觉"
你的品味!
I mean, really, Flap!
"Validate my feelings." Your taste!

1084
01:35:48,205 --> 01:35:51,409
但是医生说--
把它取出来感觉会更好
What the doctor said,
feeling good when it turns out...

1085
01:35:51,500 --> 01:35:55,083
不!忘了它吧,
我不会让你好受的!
我太生气了
No! Forget it, I won't make you
feel better, I'm too mad.

1086
01:35:55,171 --> 01:35:56,998
开饭!
Dinner!

1087
01:36:12,813 --> 01:36:16,645
亲爱的,你得了--
- 恶性的
Dear, you have a malignancy.

1088
01:36:22,490 --> 01:36:25,159
再说一遍?
-恶性的
- Say it again?
- Malignancy.

1089
01:36:28,746 --> 01:36:33,242
罗西,
我们的女儿遇上麻烦了
Rosie... our girl is in trouble.

1090
01:36:33,334 --> 01:36:35,955
她得了恶性肿瘤
She has a cyst that's malignant.

1091
01:36:36,045 --> 01:36:40,588
他们把她带去
在林肯的一家医院
They're taking her to a hospital
in Lincoln, Nebraska.

1092
01:36:47,265 --> 01:36:49,756
我们会让她
回家几天
We'll release her in a few days.

1093
01:36:49,850 --> 01:36:53,266
我们会好好护理她的
We do more and more
on an outpatient basis.

1094
01:36:53,354 --> 01:36:56,937
除非肿瘤扩大,
她都无需回医院
We shouldn't need to take her back,
unless the illness escalates.

1095
01:36:57,024 --> 01:36:59,100
但你什么也没告诉我
But you're not telling me anything.

1096
01:36:59,193 --> 01:37:01,731
你对什么还不明白?
What are you confused about?

1097
01:37:01,821 --> 01:37:04,442
她怎么样了？
How is she?

1098
01:37:04,532 --> 01:37:08,446
我告诉大家做最好
做最坏的打算
I tell people to hope for the best
and prepare for the worst.

1099
01:37:10,413 --> 01:37:12,701
他们让你如此悲观?
And they let you get away with that?

1100
01:37:13,875 --> 01:37:18,335
瞧,你这么悲观是不对的
Look, you're wrong to see everything
as so desperate and serious.

1101
01:37:18,421 --> 01:37:22,715
这给艾玛没有什么意义
And it won't do your daughter any
good to get those signals, either.

1102
01:37:28,472 --> 01:37:30,845
现在还有什么问题？
What's wrong now?

1103
01:37:31,517 --> 01:37:35,431
我对那医生生气
你有点过于伤悲了
I'm so frustrated with that doctor.
But it boils down to this.

1104
01:37:35,521 --> 01:37:39,389
你没必要再呆在这里
You're getting out and
you don't have to stay here again.

1105
01:37:39,483 --> 01:37:43,184
除非肿瘤扩大
我一点都不觉得自己生病了
Unless the illness spreads.
I really don't feel sick.

1106
01:37:43,279 --> 01:37:47,775
嘿,艾玛
去纽约吧,我请你
Hey, Emma. Come to New York
for a visit. My treat.

1107
01:37:48,618 --> 01:37:52,567
好极了我们得看看
看看这封来自孩子们的信
Great. We'll have to see.
Look at these letters from the kids.

1108
01:37:52,663 --> 01:37:56,328
泰迪说他睡不着,
但梅尔尼可以
Teddy says he couldn't sleep,
but Melanie slept fine.

1109
01:37:57,168 --> 01:38:01,379
汤米觉得没有
什么需要担心的--
Tommy thinks there's nothing
to be concerned about...

1110
01:38:01,464 --> 01:38:04,999
嘿,我是认真的!
在你看医生之前你还有时间
Hey, I mean it! You have
time before you see the doctor.

1111
01:38:05,092 --> 01:38:08,010
来看看纽约
Come see New York for a few days.

1112
01:38:09,138 --> 01:38:12,139
不是个坏主意,
对你而言只是休下假
It's not a bad idea,
a vacation by yourself.

1113
01:38:12,225 --> 01:38:14,134
罗西和我
还有孩子们都在这里
Rosie and I are here with the kids.

1114
01:38:14,227 --> 01:38:17,975
利用你的空闲时间
我知道你希望去
- Take advantage of your freedom.
- I know you wanna go.

1115
01:38:18,731 --> 01:38:23,274
这和把孩子们带去
迪斯尼乐园不同
This isn't like taking those kids
to Disneyland right before the end?

1116
01:38:23,361 --> 01:38:24,771
住嘴!
Stop!

1117
01:38:25,488 --> 01:38:27,694
哦,对不起
佩特西,我开玩笑的!
- Oh, I'm sorry.
- Patsy, I'm kidding!

1118
01:38:33,955 --> 01:38:36,825
你觉得离开
孩子们好玩吗?
Do you feel funny
about leaving the kids?

1119
01:38:36,916 --> 01:38:40,415
我没有离开他们,我只是把
他们委托给他们的父亲
I'm not leaving them,
I'm entrusting them to their father.

1120
01:38:41,671 --> 01:38:45,620
哦,虽然我不会像你母亲
和罗西在城里那么长时间
Oh, I thought as long as your mother
and Rosie are in town...

1121
01:38:45,716 --> 01:38:48,587
不是他们,是你
Not them. You.

1122
01:38:59,272 --> 01:39:03,519
艾玛!看哪! 看哪! 看哪!
我们到了吗?
- Emma, look! Look! Look!
- Are we there yet?

1123
01:39:03,609 --> 01:39:07,227
天哪！真不敢相信!我在这里
很漂亮,不是吗？
- Oh, God! I can't believe I'm here!
- Isn't it beautiful?

1124
01:39:07,321 --> 01:39:11,615
我希望你见见我的朋友
没什么好友像我和你这样
I want you to meet some of my
friends. Not friends like you and I.

1125
01:39:14,412 --> 01:39:16,737
嗨
嗨
- Hi.
- Hi.

1126
01:39:16,831 --> 01:39:18,823
艾玛,这是莉兹白
Emma, this is Lizbeth.

1127
01:39:18,916 --> 01:39:22,202
嗨, 伊丽莎白
嗨,莉兹白
- Hi, Elizabeth.
- Hi. It's Lizbeth.

1128
01:39:22,295 --> 01:39:26,755
你说, "伊丽莎白"
实际上这是莉兹白
- Isn't that what I said?
- You said "Elizabeth". It's Lizbeth.

1129
01:39:26,841 --> 01:39:31,302
哦,两个名字?莉兹 白?
不,一个 莉兹白
- Oh, two names? Liz Beth?
- No, one. Lizbeth.

1130
01:39:31,387 --> 01:39:33,925
莉兹 白?
没关系!
- Lizbeth?
- Never mind.

1131
01:39:34,015 --> 01:39:37,218
这是简
谢天谢地!
- And this is Jane.
- Thank heavens!

1132
01:39:40,104 --> 01:39:41,812
