讨论永远不会结束
It was never over
whether we loved each other.

1291
01:54:08,472 --> 01:54:11,592
哦,天哪！这领带！
Oh, God! That tie!

1292
01:54:11,684 --> 01:54:14,555
难以相信你还带着它!
I can't believe you wore that!

1293
01:54:14,645 --> 01:54:17,101
找到这条领带一定很难
The mess it must've been finding it.

1294
01:54:17,189 --> 01:54:22,184
家里仍然一团糟,这是我从
找的最后一个盒子里发现的
The house still isn't in one piece.
It was in the last box I looked in.

1295
01:54:22,278 --> 01:54:24,317
我敢打赌
I'll bet.

1296
01:54:25,406 --> 01:54:27,612
上帝,你很好哄
God, you're easy to please.

1297
01:54:27,700 --> 01:54:30,903
我不知道
我干嘛不多做点什么呢？
I don't know why
I couldn't do more of it.

1298
01:54:33,205 --> 01:54:35,779
我很高兴我们在聊天,
只是指我
I'm so glad we're talking, I just am.

1299
01:54:35,875 --> 01:54:40,453
这对我意义重大,
我们仍然能像现在这样
It just means so much to me that
we can still feel like this, so much.

1300
01:54:40,546 --> 01:54:42,918
我发誓
I swear...

1301
01:54:46,928 --> 01:54:49,383
听着,我累了
Listen, I am getting tired.

1302
01:54:50,848 --> 01:54:54,264
只需告诉我,
你真的想抚养他们？
Just tell me, hon,
you really want to raise 'em?

1303
01:55:07,365 --> 01:55:11,908
我从未想过放弃孩子
I never thought I was the sort of man
who'd give up his kids.

1304
01:55:11,994 --> 01:55:14,070
这是份很累的工作
It's a lot of work.

1305
01:55:15,206 --> 01:55:19,535
既然你觉得这是很艰难的事,
那就别希望那会简单
As hard as you think it is,
you end up wishing it were that easy.

1306
01:55:21,712 --> 01:55:23,539
你希望他们在哪里呢？
Where do you want them?

1307
01:55:23,631 --> 01:55:26,383
我不想让珍妮丝来带他们
I don't want them
to end up with Janice.

1308
01:55:29,095 --> 01:55:31,171
嗯,她并没那么糟糕
Well, she's not so bad.

1309
01:55:37,019 --> 01:55:40,602
我也不认为他们该和你在一起,
亲爱的
I really don't think
they should be with you, honey.

1310
01:55:46,445 --> 01:55:48,687
嗯,
Well...

1311
01:55:49,824 --> 01:55:52,231
实话告诉你,
To tell you the honest truth...

1312
01:55:54,370 --> 01:55:56,410
我可能把事情搞得一团糟
I'd probably screw it up.

1313
01:56:00,501 --> 01:56:02,743
我真的很想念他们
I'll really miss them.

1314
01:56:07,800 --> 01:56:10,671
嗯,也许我们应该
让佩特西带他们
Well, maybe we should let
Patsy take them.

1315
01:56:10,761 --> 01:56:15,673
对我而言
夏天在纽约做研究会简单些
It'd be easy for me to work
research summers in New York.

1316
01:56:15,766 --> 01:56:21,009
不,佩特西只是想抚养梅尔尼
身为母亲,应该抚养他们
No. Patsy really only wants Melanie.
Mother should have them.

1317
01:56:22,523 --> 01:56:24,765
你随时可以去见他们
You can see them any time you want.

1318
01:56:24,859 --> 01:56:27,480
你该为他们决定一切
You'll decide things
for them and everything.

1319
01:56:27,570 --> 01:56:29,693
她会觉得那很难
She can make that very difficult.

1320
01:56:29,780 --> 01:56:31,939
她不会
She won't.

1321
01:56:36,120 --> 01:56:40,367
嗯,我想他们最好
还是由你母亲抚养吧
Well, I guess they should be
with your mother.

1322
01:56:41,626 --> 01:56:43,832
我也许会那样做的
I probably have that coming.

1323
01:57:02,063 --> 01:57:05,977
佛莱普, 明天能把
男孩们带来吗？
Flap, will you bring
the boys by tomorrow?

1324
01:57:06,067 --> 01:57:09,436
那已经在等我了
我得完成该完成的
I've got that one waiting for me.
I gotta do it.

1325
01:57:10,529 --> 01:57:12,937
好的
谢谢
- Yeah.
- Thanks.

1326
01:57:23,918 --> 01:57:26,670
来吧,佩特西
我得做好准备
Come on, Pats, I gotta get ready.

1327
01:57:26,754 --> 01:57:29,708
佩特西
化妆!
Patsy. Make-up!

1328
01:57:33,844 --> 01:57:36,964
这样说是不是太糟糕了
我无法忍受看你母亲
Is it terrible to say
I can't stand seeing your mother

1329
01:57:37,056 --> 01:57:39,096
爱抚那小女孩?
get her hands on that little girl?

1330
01:57:39,183 --> 01:57:42,184
我只是想抚养那小女孩
I'd just love to raise
that little girl.

1331
01:57:47,608 --> 01:57:49,648
听着,我会让你抚养的,
Look, I'd let you,

1332
01:57:49,735 --> 01:57:52,357
但泰迪不能离开她
but Teddy couldn't spare her.

1333
01:57:53,281 --> 01:57:55,736
我不能再拖了,行吗?
I can't stall any more, all right?

1334
01:57:55,825 --> 01:57:58,909
你出去,
把孩子们叫进来吧
You go out there
and send the boys in.

1335
01:57:58,995 --> 01:58:01,320
嗯,我需要说点什么吗？
Well, do I get to say something ever?

1336
01:58:01,414 --> 01:58:02,528
不用
No.

1337
01:58:06,002 --> 01:58:09,453
我们没必要那样做,对吗?
过来
We don't have to do that, right?
Come here.

1338
01:58:14,093 --> 01:58:16,584
你会好的
会的
You'll be fine. You will.

1339
01:58:22,351 --> 01:58:24,178
就这些
It's just this...

1340
01:58:27,982 --> 01:58:30,307
你是我的榜样, 艾玛
You're my touchstone, Emma.

1341
01:58:32,612 --> 01:58:34,438
男孩们
The boys.

1342
01:59:17,281 --> 01:59:20,033
嗨
进来吧
Hi. Come on.

1343
01:59:20,409 --> 01:59:25,404
我爱你我想念你,
我要你回家
I love you. I miss you.
God, I want you to come home.

1344
01:59:26,624 --> 01:59:28,533
把门关上
Close the door.

1345
01:59:28,751 --> 01:59:31,538
天哪,你们看起来
都长大了
God, you both look so gigantic to me.

1346
01:59:32,922 --> 01:59:35,543
我猜我吓着你们了
I guess I look pretty bad to you.

1347
01:59:35,633 --> 01:59:37,672
没那么糟糕
Not so bad.

1348
01:59:41,597 --> 01:59:45,547
你们俩都有漂亮的眼睛
你们头发太长了
You both have beautiful eyes
and your hair's too long.

1349
01:59:45,643 --> 01:59:49,094
我不想管的,但
把头发剪了,好吗？
I don't care about the back
but keep your bangs cut, OK?

1350
01:59:49,188 --> 01:59:52,438
太长了
这只是观念问题
- It's too long.
- That's a matter of opinion.

1351
01:59:52,525 --> 01:59:55,194
留短发,好吗?
Just keep it short, all right?

1352
01:59:55,278 --> 01:59:57,104
你好点了吗?
Are you getting well?

1353
02:00:01,450 --> 02:00:02,993
抬头
Look up.

1354
02:00:03,077 --> 02:00:06,078
很包歉,
我对此无能为力
I'm sorry about this
but I can't help it.

1355
02:00:06,163 --> 02:00:09,164
我不能说太久,要不我会太悲伤的
I can't talk too long
or I'll get real upset.

1356
02:00:11,794 --> 02:00:14,830
我要你们结交朋友
I want you to make a lot of friends.

1357
02:00:14,922 --> 02:00:20,925
对女孩们好些
因为她们会对你们很重要,
我发誓
And be real nice to the girls cos
they'll be important to you, I swear.

1358
02:00:21,012 --> 02:00:24,630
我们不害怕和女孩交往
什么使你那样想?
We're not afraid of girls,
what makes you think that?

1359
02:00:24,724 --> 02:00:27,475
以后也许会,
我不相信
- Well, you may be later on.
- I doubt it.

1360
02:00:27,560 --> 02:00:30,644
你干嘛不闭嘴?
闭嘴!
你给我闭嘴!
- Why don't you shut up? Shut up!
- You shut up.

1361
02:00:30,730 --> 02:00:33,600
泰迪,亲我一口
过来
Teddy, give me a kiss, come on.

1362
02:00:37,486 --> 02:00:40,404
汤米, 乖点
乖
Tommy, you be sweet. Be sweet.

1363
02:00:42,325 --> 02:00:46,239
别假装你还恨着我
这样做很愚蠢
And stop trying to pretend
like you hate me. It's silly.

1364
02:00:47,705 --> 02:00:49,330
我爱你
I like you.

1365
02:00:49,415 --> 02:00:52,784
那就好好听着
什么?
- Then listen especially close.
- What?

1366
02:00:52,877 --> 02:00:55,119
认真听?
我所说的
- Listen real hard?
- I said what.

1367
02:00:57,757 --> 02:01:00,462
我知道你喜欢我
我知道
I know you like me. I know it.

1368
02:01:02,220 --> 02:01:06,549
去年或前两年,
你装作恨我
For the last year or two,
you've pretended like you hate me.

1369
02:01:08,226 --> 02:01:12,437
但我非常爱你
就像我爱其他人一样爱着你
But I love you very much,
as much as I love anybody,

1370
02:01:12,521 --> 02:01:14,810
就像爱惜我自己一样
as much as I love myself.

1371
02:01:14,899 --> 02:01:19,810
过些年,当我不再纠缠你
And in a few years when I haven't
been around to irritate you,

1372
02:01:19,904 --> 02:01:22,193
你会记得
you're gonna remember.

1373
02:01:22,281 --> 02:01:27,572
你会记得我给你买棒球手套,
记得我们吵架,
You'll remember when I bought the
baseball glove when we were broke

1374
02:01:27,662 --> 02:01:29,785
或者我给你读故事
or when I read you those stories,

1375
02:01:29,872 --> 02:01:34,368
又或者我让你出去玩,
而不是去割草－－太多事情
or when I let you goof off instead
of mowing the lawn, lots of things.

1376
02:01:34,460 --> 02:01:38,327
你会发现你爱着我
You're gonna realise
that you love me,

1377
02:01:38,422 --> 02:01:43,084
也许你会觉得很糟糕,因为你
没有告诉过我,但不要那样认为
and maybe you'll feel badly because
you never told me, but don't.

1378
02:01:45,471 --> 02:01:47,511
我知道你爱着我
I know that you love me.

1379
02:01:50,393 --> 02:01:54,141
所以不要那样做,
好吗?
好的!
- So don't do that to yourself, OK?
- OK!

1380
02:01:55,690 --> 02:01:58,477
好吗?
我说了,好的!
- OK?
- I said OK.

1381
02:02:01,988 --> 02:02:03,945
很好,
你们要自力更生
OK, you two should run along.

1382
02:02:04,031 --> 02:02:05,858
保重
Take care.

1383
02:02:07,952 --> 02:02:09,612
来,亲我一口
Give me a kiss.

1384
02:02:13,374 --> 02:02:17,586
我很害怕,但
我想我会好起来的,不是吗?
I was so scared,
but I think it went well, don't you?

1385
02:02:19,297 --> 02:02:21,289
嗯?
Yeah?

1386
02:02:33,686 --> 02:02:37,518
汤米,如果你想找人聊天
爸爸会认真听的
Tommy, if you need to talk,
your dad will listen.

1387
02:02:37,607 --> 02:02:40,477
他很聪明,
你知道的
He's a very smart man, you know.

1388
02:02:41,152 --> 02:02:45,944
就那样说,"爸爸,我感到困惑,
我需要和你谈谈"
Just say, "Dad, I'm confused.
I need to have a talk."

1389
02:02:50,036 --> 02:02:53,701
你知道的,
和我一起住的男孩
You know, I met this boy back in
River Oaks where I live.

1390
02:02:53,789 --> 02:02:57,372
告诉我休斯顿童子军是最好的
He said the Cub Scouts in Houston
are the best ever.

1391
02:02:57,460 --> 02:03:01,707
我们从没当过童子军
我们的妈妈懒得去管这些
We were never scouts, our mother
was too lazy to check it out.

1392
02:03:03,424 --> 02:03:05,417
别跑了! 停下!
No! Stop!

1393
02:03:06,469 --> 02:03:08,508
来吧!
别跑了!
Come on! Stop it!

1394
02:03:08,596 --> 02:03:10,007
别跑了!
No!

1395
02:03:10,097 --> 02:03:14,095
听我说!听我说!
行了, 汤姆
Listen to me! Listen. It's OK, Tom.

1396
02:03:14,185 --> 02:03:18,977
没事了
嘿!停下!
It's OK. Now...
Hey! Stop it!

1397
02:03:19,982 --> 02:03:25,024
对不起,
我无法忍受听到
尤其批评你母亲
I'm sorry, but I just can't have you
criticising your mother around me.

1398
02:04:36,350 --> 02:04:39,137
霍顿先生
霍顿先生
Mr Horton. Mr Horton?

1399
02:04:39,228 --> 02:04:41,268
她走了
She's gone.

1400
02:05:09,300 --> 02:05:11,838
天哪,我太蠢了
我太蠢了
Oh, God, I'm so stupid. So stupid...

1401
02:05:11,928 --> 02:05:13,303
我以为--
Somehow I thought...

1402
02:05:13,387 --> 02:05:17,006
以为她走的那一刻,
Somehow I thought
when she finally went,

1403
02:05:17,099 --> 02:05:19,590
就是一种解脱
that it would be a relief.

1404
02:05:20,978 --> 02:05:23,849
噢,我的小甜心!
Oh, my sweet, little darling!

1405
02:05:31,322 --> 02:05:35,818
噢, 亲爱的
没比这更难的了
没有--
Oh, dear. There's nothing harder.
There's nothing...

1406
02:05:47,129 --> 02:05:48,956
要蛋糕吗?
Do you want some cake?

1407
02:06:05,189 --> 02:06:09,057
你干嘛站在这里?
我不知道
- Why are you standing over here?
- I don't know.

1408
02:06:10,486 --> 02:06:13,357
想和我坐一起？
You wanna come over and sit with me?

1409
02:06:19,370 --> 02:06:22,454
一切都会好起来的, 汤米
Everything's gonna be
all right, Tommy.

1410
02:06:39,390 --> 02:06:44,633
啊,在休斯顿
有一流的舞蹈学校
There's fantastic
dance schools in Houston.

1411
02:06:44,729 --> 02:06:49,604
击打乐?
击打乐,芭蕾,杂技--
- Tap?
- Tap, ballet, aerobics...

1412
02:06:50,693 --> 02:06:52,567
你想要的一切
Anything you want.

1413
02:06:52,653 --> 02:06:54,860
到这边来看你爸爸
Come over here and see your dad.

1414
02:06:54,947 --> 02:06:58,399
他认识一个漂亮的女孩
不是吗?
He really knows a pretty girl,
doesn't he?

1415
02:06:58,492 --> 02:07:00,532
对他而言她太老了
She's too old for him.

1416
02:07:00,620 --> 02:07:05,744
你想吃野兔肉吗?
到爸爸那里去吃
Are you eating a wet bunny? Here.
Better go on over to Dad and eat it.

1417
02:07:17,178 --> 02:07:20,013
嗨, 佛恩
最近怎么样啊?
Hi, Vern. How are you doing here?

1418
02:07:41,994 --> 02:07:43,738
嗨,
Hi.

1419
02:07:48,042 --> 02:07:50,711
我知道你是游泳好手
I understand you're a swimmer.

1420
02:07:51,963 --> 02:07:53,789
我也是
Me, too.

1421
02:07:53,881 --> 02:07:57,167
但你是宇航员,
不是吗?
But you're an astronaut, right?

1422
02:07:57,260 --> 02:08:00,344
我是宇航员,
又是游泳好手
I'm an astronaut and a swimmer.

1423
02:08:03,391 --> 02:08:05,798
很好看的西装啊
Pretty good-looking suit, there.

1424
02:08:07,937 --> 02:08:10,854
坐近点再近点
A little closer. A little closer.

1425
02:08:11,482 --> 02:08:13,309
再近点
A little closer.

1426
02:08:13,442 --> 02:08:15,898
想看看我的泳池吗?
Do you want to see my pool?

1427
02:08:17,029 --> 02:08:21,608
我不知道现在是否是合适的时机--
你知道的,葬礼还有一切--
I don't know if the time is right.
You know, funeral and everything.

1428
02:08:21,701 --> 02:08:24,951
噢,我想是吧
来吧
Oh, I think it is. Come on.

1429
02:08:25,037 --> 02:08:30,992
我会向你展示世界上最著名的
啊, 空中漫步
I'll show you the internationally
infamous... uh... Breedlove crawl.

1430
02:08:31,085 --> 02:08:34,703
在太空里学会的
Just a little stroke
I picked up out in space.

